Package cs351.project2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColorSelector
    ColorSelector is tasked with providing methods to get different color values from the target image.
    ConsoleGUIWrapper
    This is a very simple "GUI" that serves as an wrapper so that the engine can keep working even when it is in console mode.
    Engine
    This implementation of EvolutionEngine currently manages the entire program.
    EvolutionLoop
    This is where the whole application starts and contains the main loop.
    EvolutionLoopConsole
    This performs the same base functionality as EvolutionLoop but provides a way of operating outside of the JavaFX thread without a real GUI.
    FitnessCalculator
    Given a target image and a genome, this will calculate the fitness (but not set it) for the genome in question.
    GamePopulation
    GamePopulation is called by EvolutionLoop.
    GameWindow
    GameWindow creates the GUI.
    GameWindow.Genes
    Genes is an internal class that is used and regulated by the "Show Genome Table" button.
    Histogram
    Extracts data from an image so it can be used for comparisons.
    OrderedGenomeList
    An OrderedGenomeList provides an easy way for storing Genomes and for maintaining their order.
    TriangleRenderer
    Draws triangles to a buffered image.
